Aurora.Naperville Township, DuPage County, Illi:
Naperville Township is one of nine townships in DuPage County, Illinois, USA. As of the 2010 census, its population was 100,019 and it contained 39,999 housing units.


== Geography ==
According to the 2010 census, the township has a total area of 35.89 square miles (93.0 km2), of which 34.95 square miles (90.5 km2) (or 97.38%) is land and 0.94 square miles (2.4 km2) (or 2.62%) is water.
